title: If Only They Could Talk And It Shouldnt Happen To A Vet
description:
If Only They Could Talk And It Shouldnt Happen To A Vet 
            - Abridged and Read by James Herriot -

James herriots wonderfully entertaining books about his career as a veterinary
surgeon in the rugged Yorkshire Dales
are sensational best-sellers in Britain and America and the subject of two successful films. All those things that shouldnt happen to a vet did in fact happen to herriot, and heres the author himself tells ou his story - an account which is both hilarious and memorable.

Recorded at his home in Yorkshire, this is an abridgement of Herriots first two novels. The narrative is rich in warmth and hmumor and it is easy to understand why
james herriot has become such a popular and well - loved author.

Read by James Herriot
